        "title": "Publish public Plugin Inspector findings",
        "body": "## Summary\n- Adds synchronous Plugin Inspector gating to package publish: hard findings block upload/CLI/CI immediately; warning-only findings publish successfully.\n- Generalizes inspector warnings into public plugin findings with release/version, severity, inspector version, target OpenClaw version, scan source, and notification dedupe.\n- Adds a public plugin Warnings section/counts, dashboard finding-count links, CLI warning output, rich HTML email templates, and local UI/CLI/email proof coverage.\n- Adds a single nightly GitHub workflow that runs latest `@openclaw/plugin-inspector@latest`, claims bounded batches, fetches protected scan artifacts without download metrics, persists warning/error findings, and triggers once-per-release owner email.\n\n## Review Fixes Accepted\n- Protected nightly artifact fetches so scans do not inflate public download metrics.\n- Retried owner email when findings already exist but no notification row was created after a transient send failure.\n- Unwrapped legacy ZIP `package/` directories before nightly scanning to avoid false findings.\n- Kept worker infrastructure failures out of public findings and made them fail the workflow/artifact only.\n\n## Tests\n- `bunx convex codegen`\n- `bun run format && bunx vitest run src/__tests__/package-publish-workflow.test.ts --testNamePattern \"nightly\"`\n- `bunx vitest run convex/packageInspectorHttp.test.ts convex/packages.public.test.ts src/__tests__/package-publish-workflow.test.ts --testNamePattern \"package inspector|Plugin Inspector|nightly|claim|email|artifact|workflow\"`\n- `bunx vitest run convex/packageInspectorHttp.test.ts convex/packages.public.test.ts src/__tests__/package-detail-route.test.tsx packages/clawhub/src/cli/commands/packages.test.ts`\n- `bun run ci:static`\n- `bun run ci:unit`\n- `bun run ci:types-build`\n- `bun run ci:packages`\n- `bun run ci:e2e-http`\n- `AUTOREVIEW_AUTO_TESTS=0 .agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode auto` clean\n\n## Proof Artifacts\n- UI hard-error form: `test-results/local-auth-plugin-inspecto-391a1--publishes-warning-findings-chromium/01-upload-hard-error.png`\n- UI warning publish success: `test-results/local-auth-plugin-inspecto-391a1--publishes-warning-findings-chromium/02-upload-warning-success.png`\n- Dashboard finding count: `test-results/local-auth-plugin-inspecto-391a1--publishes-warning-findings-chromium/03-dashboard-warning-count.png`\n- Public Warnings tab: `test-results/local-auth-plugin-inspecto-391a1--publishes-warning-findings-chromium/04-plugin-public-warnings.png`\n- UI MP4: `test-results/local-auth-plugin-inspecto-391a1--publishes-warning-findings-chromium/plugin-inspector-flow.mp4`\n- CLI output proof: `.artifacts/plugin-inspector-proof/cli-output-proof.png`\n- Email preview proof: `.artifacts/plugin-inspector-proof/email-preview.png`\n",
